title: 820-00164a Fan spin no brain?

Don't forget to fix Fsys checksum, if you change serial number.

title: 820-00164a Fan spin no brain?
message:
Check all TPAD_SPI traces and resistors.

Be aware of TPAD_INTWAKE marking; only SPLIT, or SHARED components can be placed at same time!
So remove R4844, if R4841 was already on the board.

Post U4810 voltages, in OSX.
